sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant L as Leader (client)
    participant S as Server (authoritative Sim)
    participant M as Members (clients)
    Note over L,M: Party / raid already formed (PartyMachine, session A1)
    L->>S: readyCheck command (leader only)
    S->>S: validate caller is leader, anti-spam cooldown
    S-->>L: readyCheckStarted (you started it)
    S-->>M: readyCheckStarted { fromName, expires }
    Note over M: HUD shows a Ready prompt plus a countdown (~30s)
    M->>S: readyCheckRespond (ready or not ready)
    S->>S: record each member status, timeout counts as not ready
    S-->>L: readyCheckUpdate { pid, status }
    S-->>M: readyCheckUpdate { pid, status }
    Note over L,M: Party frames show a green check or red X per member
    S-->>L: readyCheckResult { allReady }
    S-->>M: readyCheckResult { allReady }
